			{
				"id": "http://fff.micro.blog/2026/03/06/stoot-instancehachydermio-id.html",
				
				"content_html": "\n\t\t\n\t\t\t<blockquote class=\"toot-blockquote\" cite=\"https://hachyderm.io@evacide/status/116169564002012114\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"toot-header\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<a class=\"toot-profile\" href=\"https://hachyderm.io/@evacide\" rel=\"noopener\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<img\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\tsrc=\"https://media.hachyderm.io/accounts/avatars/110/023/534/681/636/317/original/592205ed198bf44a.jpg\"\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\talt=\"Mastodon avatar for @evacide@hachyderm.io\"\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\tloading=\"lazy\"\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\taria-hidden=\"true\"\n\t\t\t\t\t\t/>\n\t\t\t\t\t</a>\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"toot-author\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<a class=\"toot-author-name\" href=\"https://hachyderm.io/@evacide\" rel=\"noopener\">evacide</a>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<a class=\"toot-author-handle\" href=\"https://hachyderm.io/@evacide\" rel=\"noopener\">@evacide@hachyderm.io</a>\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t</div><p>The data from your Meta Ray Bans is used to train Meta&#39;s AI, which most people don&#39;t understand means that humans are looking at the most intimate details of their lives. <a href=\"https://www.svd.se/a/K8nrV4/metas-ai-smart-glasses-and-data-privacy-concerns-workers-say-we-see-everything\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" translate=\"no\"><span class=\"invisible\">https://www.</span><span class=\"ellipsis\">svd.se/a/K8nrV4/metas-ai-smart</span><span class=\"invisible\">-glasses-and-data-privacy-concerns-workers-say-we-see-everything</span></a></p><a href=\"https://www.svd.se/a/K8nrV4/metas-ai-smart-glasses-and-data-privacy-concerns-workers-say-we-see-everything\" rel=\"'noopener\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"toot-card\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"toot-card-image\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img src=\"https://media.hachyderm.io/cache/preview_cards/images/046/997/366/original/aa63eade7a6a9ab1.jpeg\" alt=\"Card image from hachyderm.io toot 116169564002012114\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"toot-card-image-image\" />\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"toot-card-content\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p class=\"card-title\">Meta’s AI Smart Glasses and Data Privacy Concerns: Workers Say “We See Everything”</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p class=\"card-description\">Bank details, sex and naked people who seem unaware they are being recorded. Behind Meta’s new smart glasses lies a hidden workforce, uneasy about peering into the most intimate parts of other people’s lives.</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</a>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"toot-footer\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<a href=\"https://hachyderm.io/@evacide/116169564002012114\" class=\"toot-date\" rel=\"noopener\">6:47 AM • March 4, 2026</a>&nbsp;<span class=\"pokey\">(UTC)</span>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t</blockquote>\n",
